<p><span class="legacy-font legacy-font--size-1 legacy-font--face-futura">The innovative Website allows you to play with their 'funny' money. (They give you $1,000,000 to start.) Your selection of players from virtually all major sports and their popularity among the 80,000 Wall Street Sports gamers determine whether your million dollars grows or diminishes.</span></p>
